[[Image:pennyfarthingpresslogo.jpg|right|The Penny-Farthing Press logo.]]
'''Penny-Farthing Press''' is a comic book publishing company located in [[Houston, Texas]], in the [[United States]]. Started in 1998 with "a plan to create comic books and children's books that exemplified quality storytelling, artwork, and printing," Penny-Farthing has expanded from its single original title, '''The Victorian''', to six comic series, including '''Captain Gravity''', '''[[Decoy (comics)|Decoy]]''', '''The Loch''', '''Para''', and '''Zendra'''.

